# Test Earthquake API Endpoints

### Get all earthquakes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes

### Get earthquake by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes/1

### Get earthquake statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes/stats

### Create new earthquake
POST http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "magnitude": 4.5,
  "location": "Cebu",
  "depth": 12.3,
  "date_time": "2024-01-20 10:30:00",
  "latitude": 10.3157,
  "longitude": 123.8854,
  "source": "PHIVOLCS"
}

### Update earthquake
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "magnitude": 5.5,
  "location": "Updated Batangas"
}

### Delete earthquake
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes/4

### Get earthquakes with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes?minMagnitude=5.0&location=Batangas&limit=5&page=1